 Palmer (Arrowverse)|Ray Palmer / Atom]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Melissa Benoist]]<ref name=\"EmpireReview\" />\n| [[Kara Danvers (Arrowverse)|Kara Zor-El / Kara Danvers / Supergirl]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | Christina Brucato<ref name=\"Brucato\" />\n| [[Lily Stein (Arrowverse)|Lily Stein]]\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Donnelly Rhodes]] and Jacob Richter (young)<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ibtimes.ph/dc-legends-tomorrow-invasion-recap-cw-arrow-flash-supergirl-5166 |title='Legends Of Tomorrow' 'Invasion!' Recap: Mick, Nate & Amaya Bring Cisco & Felicity Aboard The Waverider [VIDEOS] |last=Somosot |first=Janice |website=International Business Time |publisher=IBT Media Inc. |access-date=January 7, 2018}}</ref>\n| <!--Any addition of Agent Smith here will be reverted; the name was used jokingly in the episode. Thank you.-->\"Glasses\"<ref name=\"Glasses\" />\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n<!--End of The Flash credits-->\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Echo Kellum]]<ref name=\"EmpireReview\" />\n| [[Curtis Holt (Arrowverse)|Curtis Holt / Mister Terrific]]\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Paul Blackthorne]]<ref name=\"EmpireReview\" />\n| [[Quentin Lance]]\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n| {{CNone}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Nick Zano]]<ref name=\"EmpireReview\" />\n| [[Nathan Heywood (Arrowverse)|Nathan Heywood / Steel]]\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Amy Pemberton (actress)|Amy Pemberton]]<ref name=\"EmpireReview\" /><ref name=\"ArrowCast\" />\n| [[Gideon (Legends of Tomorrow)|Gideon]]\n| {{CNone}}\n| {{CGuest|Co-starring}}\n| {{CMain|Main}}