ators-set-for-post-crossover-appearance-on-supergirl/ |archive-date=November 30, 2016 |access-date=November 29, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LyndaCarter\">{{Cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/2016/11/30/supergirls-lynda-carter-could-have-been-on-the-flash-in-the-inva/ |title=Supergirl's Lynda Carter Could Have Been on The Flash in the Invasion! Crossover |last=Burlingame |first=Russ |date=November 29, 2016 |website=Comicbook.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202145420/http://comicbook.com/2016/11/30/supergirls-lynda-carter-could-have-been-on-the-flash-in-the-inva |archive-date=December 2, 2016 |access-date=November 30, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"DominatorsReason\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2016/11/30/why-the-cws-big-arrowverse-crossover-adapts-invasion-and-the-dominators |title=Why The CW's Big Arrowverse Crossover Adapts 'Invasion!' and the Dominators |last=Schwartz |first=Terri |date=November 30, 2016 |website=[[IGN]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161130191200/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/11/30/why-the-cws-big-arrowverse-crossover-adapts-invasion-and-the-dominators |archive-date=November 30, 2016 |access-date=November 30, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Arrow100Footage\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/29/arrow-100-episode-spoilers |title=Arrow boss previews Matrix-esque 100th episode |last=Abrams |first=Natalie |date=November 29, 2016 |website=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201064532/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/29/arrow-100-episode-spoilers |archive-date=December 1, 2016 |access-date=November 30, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AirportFilming\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sf3-Y4noqXs |title=The Flash  Heroes v Aliens&nbsp;\u2013 Behind The Teams  The CW |date=November 28, 2016 |last=The CW Television Network |author-link=The CW |access-date=November 29, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204231438/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sf3-Y4noqXs |archive-date=February 4, 2017 |work=YouTube |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"FlashProduction\">{{Cite web |url=http://thefutoncritic.com/listings/20161116cw02/ |title=(#308) \"Invasion!\" |website=[[The Futon Critic]] |access-date=November 17, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ArrowProduction\">{{Cite tweet |number=777859705548922880 |user=mguggenheim |title=We're in prep. @GBerlanti @MericlesHappen @JamesBamford |author=Marc Guggenheim |date=September 19, 2016 |access-date=September 19, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LoTProduction\">{{Cite tweet |number=780904032546070528 |user=mguggenheim |title=Production begins today on Part 2 of this year's Arrow/Flash/Legends/Supergirl crossover. @philklemmer @GBerlanti @gregorythesmith |author=Marc Guggenheim |date=September 27, 2016 |access-date=September 28, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<!-- VISUAL EFFECTS -->\n\n<ref name=\"Encore\">{{Cite web |url=http://mashable.com/2016/11/29/the-flash-invasion-crossover-flashpoint-wally/#eDaCIdyz7Sq3 |title=Hey, comic book fans, did you catch this Super 'Flash' easter egg? |last=Prudom |first=Laura |date=November 29, 2016 |website=[[Mashable]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201131126/http://mashable.com/2016/11/29/the-flash-invasion-crossover-flashpoint-wally/ |archive-date=December 1, 2016 |access-date=November 30, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"TommyRoyHolograms\">{{Cite web |url=https://comicbook.com/dc/2016/11/30/how-colton-haynes-and-colin-donnell-appeared-on-arrows-100th-epi/ |title=How Colton Haynes and Colin Donnell Appeared on Arrow's 100th Episode |last=Burlingame |first=Russ |date=November 30, 2016 |website=Comicbook.com |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201143926/http://comicbook.com/dc/2016/11/30/how-colton-haynes-and-colin-donnell-appeared-on-arrows-100th-epi/ |archive-date=December 1, 2016 |access-date=November 30, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ProducersDominators\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbr.com/guggenheim-kreisberg-explain-invasion-dominators-cw-crossover/ |title=Guggenheim & Kreisberg Explain Why Invasion! was the Right Story for CW Crossover |last=Ching |first=Albert |date=November 30, 2016 |website=[[Comic Book Resources]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201210835/http://www.cbr.com/guggenheim-kreisberg-explain-invasion-dominators-cw-crossover/ |archive-date=December 1, 2016 |access-date=November 30, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<!-- BROADCAST -->\n\n<ref name=\"EWCoverNov2016\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/09/flash-green-arrow-supergirl-cw-superheroes-crossover-cover |title=This Week's Cover: CW superheroes crossover revealed |last=Jensen |first=Jeff |date=November 9, 2016 |website=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110180445/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/11/09/flash-green-arrow-supergirl-cw-superheroes-crossover-cover |archive-date=November 10, 2016 |access-date=November 10, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<!-- MARKETING -->\n\n<ref name=\"Trailer\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.newsarama.com/31972-supergirl-flash-arrow-legends-heroes-v-aliens-cw-dc-crossover-trailer.html |title=Supergirl, Flash, Arrow, Legends' 'Heroes v. Aliens' DC-CW Crossover Trailer |last=Arrant |first=Chris |date=November 11, 2016 |website=[[Newsarama]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122220943/http://www.newsarama.com/31972-supergirl-flash-arrow-legends-heroes-v-aliens-cw-dc-crossover-trailer.html |archive-date=November 22, 2016 |access-date=November 21, 2016}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"CanadaCTV\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.ctv.ca/TheFlash/Video/S3E8-Preview-Heroes-Unite-In-A-3-Night-Crossover-Event-Tuesday-At-87C-On-CTV-vid1002510 |title=The Flash Preview: Heroes Unite In A 3-Night Crossover Event Tuesday At 8/7/C On CTV |website=CTV.ca |url-access=subscription |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/2016112802